highlights.text: Breizaas has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Dama Fra Bygda” is the highest at #18.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 90 days straight.
“Soda Pop” by Saja Boys, Andrew Choi, Neckwav, Danny Chung, KEVIN WOO, samUIL Lee, and KPop Demon Hunters Cast is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 13 spots at #63.
“Cali Man” by EsDeeKid and Rico Ace is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #48.
